{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "雪山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "雪夜獨行", "storyInfo": "埃琳娜在藏經閣偶遇返回的恩雅，交流後決定一同開始尋找謝拉格天災的成因。休露絲發現姐姐的留言，得知菈塔托絲與恩希歐迪斯早已在暗中有合作。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormlp", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "wind"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.7, "channel": "wind", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "wind", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "門鎖又被動過了，你就是不死心，是嗎？", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遺憾的是，我確認過搜查隊的路線，他們今天的活動範圍離這裡至少還有五公里。不要指望他們能聽到你的求救訊號。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼……", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plasticbag", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少吃點東西吧。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恢復期間不攝入足夠的食物，斷骨的恢復時間會延長大約百分之二十，留下後遺症的機率則會提升百分之三十五。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不打算傷害你，也不忍心看到一個優秀的戰士從此變成殘廢。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_255_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別假惺惺的！", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#7$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你最好立刻殺了我……", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的確有這個選擇……", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但就像我說的，我從來沒有打算做危害謝拉格的事，更沒有必要去殺害一個無辜的謝拉格人。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "卡羅琳", "content": "何況，我們能從那場雪崩中活下來本身就是奇蹟……"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "卡羅琳", "content": "用你們的話說，“耶拉岡德的庇護”，對嗎？"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為虔誠的信徒，這種時候不該更珍惜自己的生命嗎？", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_255_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你身為維多利亞的間諜，偷取謝拉格的軍事情報，還敢說不是在危害謝拉格？！", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#7$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這還真的是冤枉我了……", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#2$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為謝拉格人，你為什麼會覺得謝拉格最重要的秘密，只在於那幾艘微不足道的高速戰艦的消息？", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#9$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明口口聲聲感念著神明的恩典，但你們真的從來沒有人質疑過，你們口中的“神”是什麼？", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#9$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_255_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼……耶拉岡德就是耶拉岡德，沒有人應該質疑祂——", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#4$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說不通嗎……唉，也就是被困在這裡沒事可做才會想和你聊這個。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，不聊也罷。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#8$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那我倒是想和你聊聊。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是維多利亞的間諜，又是怎麼在萊茵生命工作了那麼久的？", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我既然已經為萊茵生命工作了這麼久，你又怎麼確信，我還是維多利亞的間諜？", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵……你要是想聽的話，我就來講一個故事吧——", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一個出生在維多利亞的孩子，她從小就對這片大地上一切規律法則充滿了好奇。她本來準備用畢生精力來研究這些現象背後的秘密。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當她苦讀十幾年，準備以皇家科學院榮譽學者的身分，前往哥倫比亞交流深造的時候……", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找上她的不是維多利亞的學術基金會，而是情報組織。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從此，她被允許可以好奇的問題，就僅局限於哥倫比亞政府的秘密文件。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是人的好奇心又如何能被限制住呢？她在挖掘哥倫比亞深藏的秘密時，真的碰巧發現了一個，可以讓她盡情滿足好奇心的機會……", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過說到底……哥倫比亞、維多利亞，都沒什麼區別。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們永遠為眼前一點蠅頭小利爭得頭破血流，費力搭建的秩序在毫無意義又你死我活的戰爭裡苟延殘喘……", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰還有餘力關心天空……或者是這片人們其實根本就不瞭解的大地？", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#10$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我只怪這一切無聊透頂。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#10$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g3_mainhall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清晨，蔓珠院藏經閣。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，還好窗戶的位置不高。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士們也去晨禱了……這種時候，觀測站正在風口浪尖上，一定要避開他們。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看看，地圖、地理志，任何能幫上忙的……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晨曦透過窗戶，薄薄地灑在斑駁的書脊上。"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜拂去眼前每一本圖書的灰塵，但方方正正的修士字體難以辨認，她開始懊悔自己沒有多帶一本謝拉格語詞典。"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的書到底是按照什麼分類的……這一本是格……格言集？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“耶拉岡德，向我，顯聖，祂，說道——”", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“不要求於我的殿，而要求於我的心。”", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚哇——！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_manybooksdrop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜驚慌地鬆開了手，厚厚的書掉落在木地板上。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隔著書架，她看到了一副藏在帽兜下驚訝的面孔，還有一把對準了自己的弩。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅……看敵人的手勢，她好像投降了，我們怎麼辦？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說誰投降了？！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不對不對，恩雅……恩雅·希瓦艾什？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……你就是聖女？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓——", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜恍然大悟般地點點頭。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要聲張，我們可以友好地聊聊，好嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜小心翼翼地點點頭。"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茱安娜，不要嚇到這位朋友，把弩收起來吧。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是她偷偷闖進蔓珠院，不像什麼好人。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣說的話，我們也是偷偷溜進來的啊……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位朋友，看起來應該是萊茵生命的人？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對！我叫埃琳娜，是能量科的研究員。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我只是想找一本謝拉格地圖，最好詳細描繪了謝拉格山脈和源石礦脈的所在……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要找到那一處特殊的礦脈，我說不定就能夠——", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……能夠什麼？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜小心翼翼地觀察著眼前這位看起來與自己年紀相仿的少女——卻是真真確確的，這個國家的領袖。"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜一時間不敢確定，自己將要說出的話是否是一種嚴重的冒犯。可是看著對方眼中單純又好奇的神情……"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我或許能夠解釋……謝拉格這次天災發生的原因！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g3_mainhall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說……謝拉格之所以千年來從未發生天災，是因為山脈中隱藏的源石礦脈？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯！環繞謝拉格的雪山中，藏有一條未被探明的源石礦脈，因此形成了某種源石能量場從而阻止了天災的形成。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絕對不可能！保護謝拉格的是耶拉岡德！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那請問，有人見過耶拉岡德嗎？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德降下過各種神蹟，許多人親眼目睹！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，這位小姐，我尊重你們的文化和這些傳說故事，但這說明不了什麼。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅僅看到了一些暫時無法解釋的現象，並不能以此證實它們背後一定有超越科學的理論支撐。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又怎麼證明是那些什麼亂七八糟的礦脈？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……簡單來說，源石之間有非常複雜的相互作用，即使如今我們也只探索到了冰山一角。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵生命這些年曾有過實驗。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一些條件下源石組成的能量場，會使得大氣中源石微塵的運動趨向於離散而非聚集，而天災的重要成因之一正是這些源石微塵。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由於實驗規模的限制，目前還不能穩定再現……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我相信，如果謝拉格有符合這些條件的源石礦脈，完全有消除天災的可能。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "埃琳娜", "content": "對此我有過詳細的計算——"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "埃琳娜", "content": "抱歉，這張地圖可以借我用一下嗎……"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sketchdraw", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜拿出筆記本，展示給對面的兩人，邊解釋著公式邊劃著線，全然不顧僅有的兩位聽眾是否能跟上她的思路。"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最終，埃琳娜在地圖上某一個山腳處的位置，信心滿滿地畫下一個圈。"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……所以，我的結論是，源石礦脈假說是對謝拉格不受天災襲擊的特殊地理環境最有力的解釋。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很確信我的演算沒有錯，只要我們證明在喀蘭聖山的這個位置，的確有源石礦脈的話，那一切都說得通了！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茱安娜只感到一陣暈眩，她偷偷瞥向恩雅，寄希望於聖女能出言駁斥這個奇談謬論。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而聖女卻沉默無言，輕輕咬著下唇。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（壓低聲音）我看不懂她寫的東西，你快點罵兩句。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是……那又如何解釋最近發生的這一場天災呢？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就又要說到，根據最新的研究結果，我懷疑在天災的前一天，有某樣來自星莢之外的東西墜落在了喀蘭聖山上。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看！這是觀測站在天災前一天得到的觀測數據，這就是那個“天外來物”墜落時發出的次聲波。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜打開了隨身攜帶的終端，螢幕上顯示出一段醒目的折線。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_medicalbeep", "channel": "a", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_line_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 6.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g3_mainhall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個“天外來物”體積和質量一定都非常巨大，很有可能是因為它墜落在了礦脈中心，使得能量場發生了偏移，最終才會誘發天災！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，這一系列異狀都是有跡可循的！才不是什麼怪力亂神的傳說！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅無法理解她聽到的話語，她感到記憶在模糊，一種微妙的連結正在斷裂。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“雅兒”。"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "熟悉的音調，是朋友，是奇蹟，還是……一場幻覺？"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，她不相信，絕不能相信。恐懼與孤獨襲捲周身，她竭盡全力才勉強抑制雙臂的顫抖。"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅，你說話啊……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……能夠理解埃琳娜小姐的想法。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我想起了《耶拉岡德》中一部分經文……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“祂的心臟即是喀蘭的心臟，群山深處的寓所。祂的心臟跳動，謝拉格的骨骼和血肉從此開始生長”。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這是經文中對謝拉格起源的描述。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們曾經都理所當然地認為，喀蘭的心臟指的就是銀心湖，連耶拉岡德的雕像都因此建在銀心湖畔。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是根據這幾天的研究發現，古籍中將“喀蘭之心”的凍結當作了一種異狀，但是銀心湖是每年都會凍結的湖泊……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來就只是個修辭手法……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不要打斷聖女大人的思考啦！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，“喀蘭之心”實際上真的另有所指呢……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿德頌大長老試圖引導我思考“拉德索恩”，但一切的關鍵其實是“喀蘭之心”……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位……埃琳娜小姐，您剛才提到了，“特殊礦脈”的中心？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，我建了一套謝拉格山脈的模型，透過計算，那個天外來物墜落的地方，大概是在……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個位置。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是……謝拉格和卡西米爾的聯合礦區？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "礦區？對吧！這就都說得通了！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事不宜遲，我們現在就去——", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下！外來者！我們還沒答應讓你在謝拉格的領地內亂跑，何況你還滿嘴對耶拉岡德不敬——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事的，茱安娜。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們從不強求他人有和我們一樣的信仰，何況現在，我們也需要解開眼前這場天災的真相……就讓她與我們同行吧。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "恩雅", "content": "埃琳娜小姐……"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "恩雅", "content": "嗯？"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在恩雅和茱安娜說話時，埃琳娜早已整理好了書架。現在她正坐在窗台上，朝恩雅和茱安娜招手。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，藏經閣正門那邊，一般也不會有人。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "x": 100.0, "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從烏雲間漏下的冰涼月光覆上陳設，菈塔托絲的房間安靜無聲。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲原本以為，自己會害怕見到她的遺物，如今卻疲憊到甚至無力傷懷。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她內心深知，前幾日和各家的交涉中，自己只是在模仿菈塔托絲的樣子。"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而越模仿，她的身影就越來越生動，如同尚未離去。"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窗外，休露絲眼中的布朗陶領地，像是多下了一場雪。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“休露絲，你看，把雪球這樣，就能丟得遠一點，你試試看。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“用不著你來教我……”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我不想變成你。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我討厭你，討厭你讓我做的每一件事。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記憶的回聲猶如山脈塌陷時的巨響，重重地壓在她的胸口。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "箱子裡堆積的契約與信件落滿灰塵，那是多年來布朗陶家長足發展的證明。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲緩緩翻過每一頁菈塔托絲留下的痕跡，她這才發現，這些關於家族產業的文件末尾，應當簽署布朗陶家主姓名的位置——"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“休露絲”"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“休露絲，你最好記得。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我是你的姐姐，將來也會是布朗陶家的家主，所以你得聽我的話，這是理所當然的。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“你要是不服氣，就證明給我看，你會比我做得更好，更適合發號施令。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“到那時……”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“休露絲，我希望，你會肩負起布朗陶家的未來。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 1.2}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一頁、兩頁……休露絲的動作急切起來。"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不停翻找著，只是確認了這些文件上無一例外地都簽署上了自己的名字。"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到在那一箱遺物的底部，她的手指觸碰到了那個回憶中的小盒子——"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屬於她們的“秘密”。"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“你記住，以後姐姐想要給你，但是不想讓大人們看到的，都在這裡。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“不許告訴任何人，這是秘密。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“秘密就是永遠都只有兩個人知道的事情，這兩個人，是我和你。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cardboard", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡面是……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊器？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲仔細觀察著手上的設備，微光照亮了她遲疑的面龐。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後一則通訊記錄……"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經拿到喀蘭貿易提供的可疑人員情報了，盯了她一整個早上，看來她可能正在準備撤離。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個聲音是……莫希？！", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幹得不錯，要盯緊她，不能讓她溜了，也絕不能讓她把手裡的資料交給別人。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是……剛剛喀蘭貿易那邊提醒，要我們小心處理，別太引人注目。", "name": "莫希"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就儘量活捉，我們還有一堆問題想好好問問這位呢。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會聯絡恩希歐迪斯，讓喀蘭貿易的人也趕去車站支援你。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道了，我儘量。", "name": "莫希"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬事小心，做得乾淨一點。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，是一則來源為喀蘭貿易的未接通訊提醒。"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊時間，為什麼是在……昨天？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……喀蘭貿易？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#5$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}